\tc1 Kasi bawa iboda.
\tc2 
\tcr3 108, 100.
\b
\p Otubolousi Yuda sola Rubeni si boda, Epereim la boda bilouyasi otubolousi.
\p 
\v 25-31 E opiliyavata, matausina bisisuaisi otalila doya miyana Dani la boda, iboda bibudaisi si kabosikaiwa osi boda wala titoulesi deli wala kasi tokaraiwaga. Ka, baisa makawala kala takasa.
\b
\tr 
\th1 Dala
\th2 Tokugwa\f e \ft (Aiesa matauna Amisadai latula, Pagieli matauna Okirana latula, Aira matauna Enani latula.)\f*
\th3 Kasi Bawa
\tr 
\tc1 Dani
\tc2 Aiesa
\tcr3 62,700
\tr 
\tc1 Asera
\tc2 Pagieli
\tcr3 41,500
